      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 67: showOriginal is local delegate state and is never reset when the delegate starts representing a different message. In a reused chat delegate, toggling one overwritten message can leak that display state into another item after scrolling or model updates. Reset it when the message identity/content changes, or make the state model-backed per message.\n```suggestion\nonIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonOriginalBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\n```",
