      "writtenOn": "2026-06-23T14:57:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Major] Line 68: isPluginOverwrite treats any strict mismatch between Body and OriginalBody as an extension overwrite. If OriginalBody is missing, null, or not populated for older/non-plugin messages, this will incorrectly show the plugin-modified indicator and toggle. Gate this on OriginalBody being a real value before comparing.\n```suggestion\nproperty bool hasOriginalBody: OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d undefined \u0026\u0026 OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d null \u0026\u0026 OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \"\"\nproperty bool isPluginOverwrite: hasOriginalBody \u0026\u0026 Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody\n```",
      "revId": "805a4e937d396cbaf4ce08d237c98418fc4d7def",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
