      "writtenOn": "2026-06-23T14:57:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: Returning OriginalBody directly bypasses the existing MessagesAdapter.parseMessage/ParsedBody path used for normal message rendering. That can produce inconsistent rendering and may expose unsanitized rich-text/HTML if the Text component interprets markup. Route the original body through the same parsing/sanitization path as Body, ideally with a separate parsed-original role/cache so toggling does not display raw user-controlled content.\n```suggestion\n// Use the same parsed/sanitized representation for OriginalBody as for Body,\n// e.g. parse OriginalBody into ParsedOriginalBody and return that here.\nif (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite) {\n    return ParsedOriginalBody;\n}\n```",
      "revId": "805a4e937d396cbaf4ce08d237c98418fc4d7def",
